title: Grateful Dead Live at Orpheum Theater on 1976-07-12
lineage: MAC >> Nakamichi CR7a => Korg MR-1000 >> DSF [1-bit 5.6448 MHz Stereo] >> Korg MR-1000 => Korg AudioGate >> WAV [24/96]
description:
Set I
The Music Never Stopped, Brown Eyed Women, Cassidy, Tennessee Jed, Minglewood Blues, Candyman, Looks Like Rain, Row Jimmy, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication, Deal, Promised Land

Set II
Sugaree, Samson & Delilah, Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-> Dancin' In The Streets-> Wharf Rat-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Around & Around, E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text:
Thanks Thanks Bob for taping, transferring & sharing.

To answer question about show not available for download: some tapers do not want what they worked so hard at to become watered down by lossy formats etc, etc. You'll also notice that it seems Bob posted these as WAV files for streaming so absolutely no compression exists.
